modName: Tame the beasts of Skyrim II plus Monster Mod V4 Compatability
summary: So about a year ago I made a compatibility mod for the mods listed in the title for an outdated version of SkyMoMod and a fan requested I make a new version so I did.Also if anyone needs a voice actor im always available.Requires Monster Mod http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35631/?   ,and Tame the Beasts II
descriptionHtml: This mod adds keywords rendering the creatures of SkyMoMod tameable.Enjoy giant extreme and immersive battles with titans of all forms then as you wear them down to low health tame them!Walk around with a fire giant,Killing mercilessly with the spirit of death itself, and conquer Skyrim from the dark wilderness.Requires Monster Mod and Tame the Beasts. Endorse all three mods if you liked it and wanna show some appreciation.Also if anyone needs a voice actor im always available.
author: Tengukari            Dogtown1 and Ironman5000 for SkyMoMod and ofcourse TheSkoomaKing and hfiani  for Tame the Beasts
